  "texts": [
    "We believe this paper serves as a timely complement to the field of object detection in traffic scenarios.",
    "Furthermore, we hope that this survey will inspire researchers, foster a better understanding of object detection in traffic scenarios, and further promote research in autonomous driving.",
    "The rest of the paper is organized as follows: in Section 2, we summarise the generic target detection algorithmic framework, and in Section 3, we categorize target detection applications according to different traffic scenario tasks and select some representative works in each category.",
    "In Section 4, the target detection algorithm optimization scheme is summarized to meet the needs of target detection and recognition applications in different traffic scenes.",
    "Section 5 classifies commonly used datasets according to different applications in traffic scenarios and summarises the evaluation criteria."
